t's important to clarify that no extra dependencies are needed since the POM handles that. I’ll also highlight the risks of API changes and potential interactions with the local repository and network.\"}]}"}, {"type": "text", "text": "{\n  \"action\": \"no_action\",\n  \"summary\": \"No extra setup is required: maven-core 2.0.7 declares the needed Maven, Plexus, Wagon, commons-cli, and classworlds dependencies transitively, and meaningful tests can exercise CLI/help/version, runtime info, diagnosers, and component contracts without Docker or special environment.\",\n  \"deterministic_setup\": [],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"The reported javac failure is caused by generated tests using constructor signatures that do not match maven-artifact 2.0.7, not by a missing dependency.\",\n    \"Tests that execute real Maven goals rather than lightweight APIs may touch user settings, the local repository, or remote artifact resolution; keep such tests self-contained with temporary directories if they are added.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0437b9b4b0869cc0016a40f1caed7c81968def8fd217859e20\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 328, "output": 1105, "cacheRead": 29184, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 30617, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782641071877, "responseId": "resp_0437b9b4b0869cc0016a40f1b086388196b01f8848d029cd94"}}
